data.description: This is a beautiful home in a distinguished Del Webb community! This home boast 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a bonus room that can be used as a study. This home was updated with granite counter tops and a tiled backsplash. This home has upgraded ceiling fans and a covered patio. This home also have the upgraded garage with the windows. This home is perfect for the person who is looking to downsize. The Del Webb community is absolutely beautiful. You will not be disappointed.
